{"tid":802951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拍LD拖 十有九散","createTime":"2018-09-01T22:20:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T23:43:37.000Z","uid":175465,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2dfe8551c71bfefc2ec70aeec6dd81ea973bd7","tid":802951,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T22:20:18.000Z","msg":"女朋友係英國讀書 拍咗兩年幾拖 覺得好夾<br />\n我呢啲小窮人只可以每日同佢whatsapp <br />\n佢瞓覺嘅時候我啱啱起身我瞓覺嘅時候 佢又岩岩起身<br />\n幫我掛住佢嘅時候佢又唔可以同我講電話因為瞓緊覺<br />\n三年到底點捱 就算比一年我都捱唔過<br />\n好想日日見到佢 好想唔開心嘅時候係佢身邊<br />\n好想好好咁照顧佢 而家打算申請wh去英國<br />\n但係又驚搵唔到工 因為佢學校同倫敦唔近<br />\n我應承左屋企人十月去到之後 三個月內搵到工 要俾家用<br />\n覺得好迷惘 fg去到嗰啲地方點會有office請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好無助 有冇人係英國wh可以分享下<br />\n又或者講下LD點樣適應時差去相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe379d1d3f296192de9a0d0c0fa238fb5c464c6","tid":802951,"uid":129987,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:21:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"750f5f21539c91300b2f5e18fa68bf0f5384e894","tid":802951,"uid":61766,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:17:40.000Z","msg":"男朋友係英國LD 左兩年<br />\n過幾日就讀完書返hk了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最緊要係自律<br />\n約左咩人去邊肯一早講定<br />\n大家信任大家<br />\n每日keep住講電話facetime"},{"pid":"6139d056bbab9e902861960b281fd780ce603f6f","tid":802951,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe379d1d3f296192de9a0d0c0fa238fb5c464c6","tid":802951,"uid":129987,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T23:21:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T20:58:35.000Z","msg":"可唔可以分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5052237c6bd55ab995851196015db855061f